{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Fulvia (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that, according to Sallust, <b><a href=\"/wiki/Fulvia_(mistress_of_Quintus_Curius)\" title=\"Fulvia (mistress of Quintus Curius)\">Fulvia</a></b> revealed the details of the <a href=\"/wiki/Catilinarian_conspiracy\" title=\"Catilinarian conspiracy\">Catilinarian conspiracy</a> to Cicero <i>(event pictured)</i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fulvia_(mistress_of_Quintus_Curius)","retrieved":1777793376452},{"title":"Manuscript Society of New York (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Manuscript_Society_of_New_York\" title=\"Manuscript Society of New York\">Manuscript Society of New York</a></b> provided opportunities to women composers at a time when such support was rarely found elsewhere?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manuscript_Society_of_New_York","retrieved":1777793376456},{"title":"Betbunia (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Betbunia_Satellite_Ground_Station\" title=\"Betbunia Satellite Ground Station\">Betbunia</a></b> is Bangladesh's first <a href=\"/wiki/Ground_station\" title=\"Ground station\">ground station</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Betbunia_Satellite_Ground_Station","retrieved":1777793376457},{"title":"La Estrella (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/La_Estrella_(Mosqueruela)\" title=\"La Estrella (Mosqueruela)\">La Estrella</a></b>, Spain, became a ghost town in 2023, after its final two permanent inhabitants moved away?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/La_Estrella_(Mosqueruela)","retrieved":1777793376459},{"title":"Roosevelt Blackmon (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Roosevelt_Blackmon\" title=\"Roosevelt Blackmon\">Roosevelt Blackmon</a></b> went from college <a href=\"/wiki/Water_boy\" title=\"Water boy\">water boy</a> to NFL player?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roosevelt_Blackmon","retrieved":1777793376484},{"title":"Race Across the World series 6 (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that a sacking meant that a <b><a href=\"/wiki/Race_Across_the_World_series_6\" title=\"Race Across the World series 6\"><i>Race Across the World</i> series&nbsp;6</a></b> spin-off announced its host with hours to spare?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Race_Across_the_World_series_6","retrieved":1777793376484},{"title":"Akilagpa Sawyerr (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that, while <b><a href=\"/wiki/Akilagpa_Sawyerr_(lawyer)\" title=\"Akilagpa Sawyerr (lawyer)\">Akilagpa Sawyerr</a></b> was a law student in London, he petitioned the <a href=\"/wiki/Judicial_Committee_of_the_Privy_Council\" title=\"Judicial Committee of the Privy Council\">Privy Council</a> on behalf of men sentenced to death in South Africa's <a href=\"/wiki/Bambatha_Rebellion\" title=\"Bambatha Rebellion\">Zulu Rebellion</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akilagpa_Sawyerr_(lawyer)","retrieved":1777793376485},{"title":"a 19th-century Chinese newspaper (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Youxi_Bao\" title=\"Youxi Bao\">a 19th-century Chinese newspaper</a></b> helped to establish a cemetery for <a href=\"/wiki/Courtesan\" title=\"Courtesan\">courtesans</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Youxi_Bao","retrieved":1777793376485},{"title":"Hannah Cruz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Lin-Manuel Miranda showed <b><a href=\"/wiki/Hannah_Cruz\" title=\"Hannah Cruz\">Hannah Cruz</a></b> a tunnel to her husband?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hannah_Cruz","retrieved":1777793376486},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<div class=\"banner-image js-proportonal-resize notheme\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;: